      static WeightedGraph GraphData.fillGraph(java.util.ArrayList<ProviderDataObject> nodes)
      This method initializes a weighted graph and then passes it to the setEdges function to fill the graph with edges, the nodes arraylist is passed as well because each edge consists of two hospital locations which will be represented by integers that correspond to the hospitals index value in the arraylist.
